snippet.title: Why The Media Stalks Meghan & Harry More Than William & Kate
snippet.description:
Ever since it was revealed that Prince Harry was dating Meghan Markle, the world has been obsessed. Unfortunately, the media attention hasn’t always been completely positive. But despite any harsh headlines, love prevailed, and the two were happily married. Interest didn’t die down from there and only grew more intense after they both left the royal family.

While the world focuses on Harry and Meghan, Prince William and Kate Middleton by comparison seem to be dodging the spotlight. How have they been able to maintain a lower profile? This is why the media stalks Meghan and Harry more than William and Kate.

#PrinceHarry #MeghanMarkle #KateMiddleton
